Package com.flipkart.bean

Class GymOwner

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.GymOwner
public class GymOwner extends Object
Represents a Gym Owner in the Flipkart system. This class contains the details and operations related to a gym owner including personal, contact, and business information.
